Insider Activity


Individual




Frederick G. Smith



Mr. Frederick G. Smith is a Director & Vice President at Sinclair Broadcast Group, Inc. and a Director & Vice President at Sinclair Television Group, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at Sinclair Broadcast Group, Inc., Freven Foundation LLC, University of Maryland, St. Joseph's Hospital, Sinclair Relief Fund, Inc., The University of Maryland Baltimore Foundation, Inc., Gerstell Development LP, Keyser Investment Group, Inc., Beaver Dam LLC, Bay Television, Inc., Cunningham Communications, Inc., Sinclair Television Group, Inc., and Gerstell Academy.
Mr. Smith was previously employed as Vice President by Sinclair Ventures, Inc. He also served on the board at Safe Waterways in Maryland and Frederick G. Smith PA.



