Frederick W. Smith

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

For the physician and surgeon in Syracuse, New York, see Frederick W. Smith (physician).
For other people named Fred Smith, see Fred Smith (disambiguation).


Frederick W. Smith


Born
Frederick Wallace Smith
(1944-08-11) August 11, 1944 (age 72)
Marks, Mississippi, U.S.


Alma mater
Yale University (BA)


Net worth
 US $4.3 billion (March 2017)[1]


